sid and nancy ( also known as sid and nancy : love kills ) is a 1986 british biopic directed by alex cox and co-written with abbe wool . the film portrays the life of sid vicious ( gary oldman ) , bassist of the seminal punk rock band the sex pistols , and his relationship with girlfriend nancy &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( chloe webb ) . the film also features supporting performances from david hayman , xander berkeley , and courtney love . the film premiered at the cannes film festival in 1986 , and was released theatrically in the united states that fall . despite failing to recoup its production budget at the box office , the film was received favourably by most critics and has attained cult classic status .